# Changes file for App-GitKtti
2.0.1  2025-09-20
    - Lint fixes

2.0.0  2025-09-10
    - MAJOR MODERNIZATION RELEASE - CPAN READY!
    - BREAKING CHANGES: Complete architecture modernization for CPAN distribution
    - Scripts renamed with gitktti- prefix (e.g., gitktti-checkout)
    - Module restructured from GitKttiUtils to App::GitKtti
    - Installation now via standard Perl/CPAN methods
    - CPAN installable with 'cpan App::GitKtti'
    - Proper Makefile.PL with dependencies and metadata
    - Professional test suite in t/ directory
    - Installation script (install.sh) with multiple options
    - Modern documentation with POD format
    - MANIFEST and META.yml files for distribution
    - FindBin support for proper library loading
    - All scripts use modern Perl practices
    - Better error handling and user feedback
    - Consistent command-line interface across all tools
    - Improved help system with --help for all commands
    - Enhanced diagnostic tool (gitktti-tests)

